```js
    const arr = ['a', '', 'b', '', 'c', '', 'd', '', 'e'];
    assert.deepEqual(
      arr.values() // creates an iterator
        .filter(x => x.length > 0)
        .drop(1)
        .take(3)
        .map(x => `=${x}=`)
        .toArray()
      ,
      ['=b=', '=c=', '=d=']
    );

    ```

```js
    assert.deepEqual(
      Map.groupBy([0, -5, 3, -4, 8, 9], x => Math.sign(x)),
      new Map()
        .set(0, [0])
        .set(-1, [-5,-4])
        .set(1, [3,8,9])
    );
    ```
